        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "perf: avoid event-loop stall during embedded_run bootstrap-context",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nFix event-loop stalls during `embedded_run` bootstrap-context that block the event loop for 14-22 seconds, causing message loss.\n\n### Root causes addressed\n\n1. **Synchronous file I/O** — `readFileSync`/`closeSync` in workspace file loading blocks the event loop while reading root bootstrap files (AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, etc.)\n2. **Unbounded glob walks** — `fs.glob` for extra bootstrap files traverses the entire workspace tree without limits, including `.git`/`node_modules` directories\n3. **Uninterrupted hook chains** — `triggerInternalHook` executes all handlers back-to-back without yielding\n\n### Changes\n\n**`src/agents/workspace.ts`**\n- Replace sync `readFileSync`/`closeSync` with callback-based async `readFdToString`/`closeFdAsync`\n- Parallelize root bootstrap file reads via `Promise.all` (previously serial `for` loop)\n- Bound glob walks: visit limit (20,000), match limit (128), `setImmediate` yield every 256 entries\n- Exclude `.git`, `node_modules`, `dist`, `.next`, `.turbo`, `__pycache__` from glob traversal\n- Suppress `closeFdAsync` rejections to avoid masking read errors on NFS/FUSE\n\n**`src/hooks/internal-hooks.ts`**\n- Add `yieldBetweenHandlers` option with `setImmediate` yield between hook handlers\n- Add per-handler timing instrumentation with handler index reporting\n- Log warnings for slow handlers exceeding 500ms threshold\n\n**`src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/attempt.ts`**\n- Instrument bootstrap-context substages (`workspace-file-load`, `hook-overrides`) with `performance.now` timing\n- Log substage durations when total bootstrap-context exceeds 2 seconds\n- Enable `yieldBetweenHandlers` for `agent:bootstrap` hook triggers\n\n**`src/agents/bootstrap-files.ts`** / **`src/agents/bootstrap-hooks.ts`**\n- Support new async workspace file loading and timing callback interfaces\n\n### Tests\n\n- `workspace.test.ts` — 3 new tests for async fd read (happy path, cache hit, fd close on failure)\n- `workspace.load-extra-bootstrap-files.test.ts` — 2 new tests for ignored directory filtering and glob match cap enforcement\n- `internal-hooks.test.ts` — 3 new tests for yield-between-handlers ordering, handler timing reporting, and slow handler warning\n\nAll existing tests pass without modification.\n\n### Performance impact\n\n- Root bootstrap file loading: serial sync → parallel async (estimated 3-5x speedup for 8 files)\n- Glob walks: unbounded → capped at 20K entries with periodic yields (prevents multi-second stalls on large workspaces)\n- Hook chains: uninterrupted → yielded (prevents monopolizing the event loop during bootstrap)\n\nCloses #87509\n",
        "branch": "fix/bootstrap-context-event-loop-stall",
